"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?41/36/42566?source=related_link\">",
"      Patient information: Vaccines for infants and children age 0 to 6 years (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
